text: Occidental Mindoro (, , , ) is a province of the Philippines. It is in the MIMAROPA region. The capital is Mamburao. Dubbed as "Marine Wonderland," the fantastic land that is Occidental Mindoro is endowed with marine beauty from its virgin forests, beautiful white sand beaches, islands and islets rich in marine life, coral gardens, mysterious caves, and cascading waterfalls.
